Job description 1:

Key Responsibilities
-Marketing Strategy - Assess the existing marketing strategy to revise and develop a comprehensive strategy, including prioritization of marketing channels (conferences/field events, ABM, social media, email, paid advertising, etc). Drive our growth via setting goals, defining target audiences, creating business cases for marketing activities based on impact, and managing the budget.
-Brand Awareness & Consistency - Develop and maintain our brand strategy, messaging and visual identity across all marketing channels and sales deliverables to enhance brand visibility, recognition, and alignment with the company’s mission.
-Integrated Campaigns & Funnels - Create messaging and successfully plan, execute, and analyze marketing campaigns (across all channels) and establish key B2B funnels to increase MQLs and achieve conversion goals or other business objectives.
-Content Creation - Lead content development and creation across all channels for the agency including sales and marketing collateral, email, website and blog, whitepapers, video, newsletter, social media, and conference/field events.
-Analytics & Reporting - Using Hubspot and other available tools, provide detailed analysis and reports on conversion metrics, campaign performance, and ROI to recommend investment in marketing activities.
-Demonstrated success growing MQLs and providing a strong ROI across all channels.
-Demonstrated success supporting MQL to SQL conversion.
-Experience creating digital assets for marketing campaigns, such as graphics, written copy, social posts.
-Experience both leading strategy and executing independently on a marketing team of one.
-Strong data analysis and prioritization skills.

