-Performance Tracking & Optimization: Monitor brand and campaign performance, including both TV and digital metrics, and refine strategies based on results to maximize impact.
-Brand Investment Management: Oversee marketing budgets strategically, ensuring optimal allocation to campaigns that deliver the highest brand and audience impact.

Skills & attributes for success:
-Self-starter with a drive to take initiatives
-People management & influencing skills
-Excellent analytical, communication & presentation skills – clarity in thought & articulation
-Passion for sports and digital engagement
-Agile & adaptable; ability to deal with ambiguity

